span>#&#160;<wbr>access&#160;<wbr>phase</wbr></wbr></span><br />\n&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr><a href=\"http://wiki.nginx.org/NginxHttpAccessModule#deny\"><span>deny</span></a>&#160;<wbr>10.32.168.49<span>;</span><br />\n&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>access_by_lua&#160;<wbr><span>\"ngx.var.age&#160;<wbr>=&#160;<wbr>ngx.var.age&#160;<wbr>*&#160;<wbr>3\"</wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></span><span>;</span><br />\n&#160;<wbr><br />\n&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr><span>#&#160;<wbr>content&#160;<wbr>phase</wbr></wbr></span><br />\n&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>echo&#160;<wbr><span>\"age&#160;<wbr>=&#160;<wbr>$age\"</wbr></wbr></span><span>;</span><br />\n&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr><span>}</span>\n</wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></pre></div>\n</div>\n<p>&#36825;&#20010;&#20363;&#23376;&#20013;&#21508;&#20010;&#37197;&#32622;&#25351;&#20196;&#30340;&#25191;&#34892;&#39034;&#24207;&#20415;&#26159;&#23427;&#20204;&#30340;&#20070;&#20889;&#39034;&#24207;&#12290;&#27979;&#35797;&#32467;&#26524;&#23436;&#20840;&#31526;&#21512;&#39044;&#26399;&#65306;</p>\n<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<div>\n<pre>\n&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>$&#160;<wbr>curl&#160;<wbr><span>\'http://localhost:8080/test\'</span><br />\n&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>age&#160;<