"after...\"</span><span>;</span><br />\n&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr><span>}</span><br />\n&#160;<wbr><br />\n&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr><a href=\"http://wiki.nginx.org/NginxHttpCoreModule#location\"><span>location</span></a>&#160;<wbr>/foo&#160;<wbr><span>{</span><br />\n&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>echo&#160;<wbr><span>\"contents&#160;<wbr>to&#160;<wbr>be&#160;<wbr>proxied\"</wbr></wbr></wbr></span><span>;</span><br />\n&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr><span>}</span>\n</wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></pre></div>\n</div>\n<p>&#27979;&#35797;&#32467;&#26524;&#34920;&#26126;&#36825;&#19968;&#27425;&#25105;&#20204;&#25104;&#21151;&#20102;&#65306;</p>\n<div dir=\"ltr\" style=\"text-align: left;\">\n<div>\n<pre>\n&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>$&#160;<wbr>curl&#160;<wbr><span>\'http://localhost:8080/test\'</span><br />\n&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>before...<br />\n&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>contents&#160;<wbr>to&#160;<wbr>be&#160;<wbr>proxied<br />\n&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>after...\n</wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></wbr></pre></div>\n</div>\n<p>&#37197;&#32622;&#25351;&#20196; <a href=\"http://wiki.nginx.org/HttpEchoModule#echo_before_body\" title=\"HttpEchoModule\">echo_before_body</a> &#21644; <a href=\"http://wiki.nginx.org/HttpEchoModule#echo_after_body\" title=\"HttpEchoModule\">echo_after_body</a> &#20043;&#25152;&#20197;&#21487;&#20197;&#21644;&#20854;&#20182;&#27169;&#22359;&#36816;&#34892;&#22312;\n<code>c