wbr></wbr></p>\n<br /><p>&#160;<wbr> &#160;<wbr><a href=\"http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_6d579ff40100wk2j.html\">Nginx &#21464;&#37327;&#28459;&#35848;&#65288;&#20108;&#65289;</a> &#20013;&#20171;&#32461;&#36807;&#30340; <a title=\"HttpSetMiscModule\" href=\"http://wiki.nginx.org/HttpSetMiscModule\">ngx_set_misc</a> &#27169;&#22359;&#30340;\n<a title=\"HttpSetMiscModule\" href=\"http://wiki.nginx.org/HttpSetMiscModule#set_unescape_uri\">\nset_unescape_uri</a> &#25351;&#20196;&#21516;&#26679;&#20063;&#36816;&#34892;&#22312; <code>rewrite</code>\n&#38454;&#27573;&#12290;&#29305;&#21035;&#22320;&#65292;<a title=\"HttpSetMiscModule\" href=\"http://wiki.nginx.org/HttpSetMiscModule\">ngx_set_misc</a>\n&#27169;&#22359;&#30340;&#25351;&#20196;&#36824;&#21487;&#20197;&#21644; <a title=\"HttpRewriteModule\" href=\"http://wiki.nginx.org/HttpRewriteModule\">ngx_rewrite</a>\n&#30340;&#25351;&#20196;&#28151;&#21512;&#22312;&#19968;&#36215;&#20381;&#27425;&#25191;&#34892;&#12290;&#25105;&#20204;&#26469;&#30475;&#36825;&#26679;&#30340;&#19968;&#20010;&#20363;&#23376;&#65306;</wbr></wbr></p>\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<div>\n<pre>\n&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr><a href=\"http://wiki.nginx.org/NginxHttpCoreModule#location\"><span>location</span></a>&#160;<wbr>/test&#160;<wbr><span>{</span><br />\n&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr><a href=\"http://wiki.nginx.org/NginxHttpRewriteModule#set\"><span>set</span></a>&#160;<wbr><span>$a</span>&#160;<wbr><span>\"hello<span>%</span>20world\"</span><span>;</span><br />\n&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>set_unescape_uri&#160;<wbr><span>$b</span>&#160;<wbr><span>$a</span><span>;</span><br />\n&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr>&#160;<wbr><a href=\"http://wiki.nginx.org/NginxHttpRewriteModule#set\"><span>set</span></a>&#160;<wbr><span>$c</span>&#160;<wbr><span>\"$b